# Another realization

Pantheon seems obsessed with one property:

Representation independence.

Meaning:

If I express the same system as

Python

English

Myth

Graph

Database

YAML

Mathematics

...the system should remain equivalent.

That reminds me of compiler intermediate representations.

LLVM doesn't care if the source language was C or Rust.

Pantheon seems to want a semantic IR for cognition.

